---
import DocsLayout from "../../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";

const nodes = [
    { num: "1", type: "Webhook", name: "Alertmanager Webhook", desc: "Recibe el POST de Alertmanager con el payload JSON de la alerta. Path: /webhook/alertmanager. Method: POST.", detail: "El payload incluye: status (firing/resolved), alerts (array), labels (severity, alertname), annotations (description, summary), startsAt." },
    { num: "2", type: "Set", name: "Extraer datos", desc: "Extrae los campos relevantes del payload: alertname, severity, description, value, labels. Los convierte en variables accesibles para los nodos siguientes.", detail: "Usa expresiones JSON: {{ $json.alerts[0].labels.alertname }}, {{ $json.status }}. Si hay multiples alertas, itera sobre el array." },
    { num: "3", type: "HTTP Request", name: "LLM Analysis", desc: "POST a OpenCode Go API con el prompt de ingenieria. Envia los datos de la alerta formateados y solicita analisis de causa raiz y acciones.", detail: "Configuracion: Method POST, URL https://opencode.ai/zen/go/v1/chat/completions, Header Authorization: Bearer {{ $env.N8N_OPENCODE_API_KEY }}." },
    { num: "4", type: "HTTP Request", name: "Discord Notification", desc: "POST al webhook de Discord con el analisis del LLM formateado en Markdown. Incluye los datos originales de la alerta y la respuesta del LLM.", detail: "El body usa Discord webhook format: { content: null, embeds: [{ title, description, color, fields, timestamp }] }. Color rojo para firing, verde para resolved." },
];
---

<DocsLayout
    title="Workflow 1: Incident Response - ITOps Automation Lab"
    description="Phase 5 del Rocky Linux ITOps Automation Lab: workflow de respuesta automatica a incidentes — Alertmanager → n8n → LLM → Discord."
    activePage="workflow-1-incident-response"
    lang="en"
    prev={{ label: "OpenCode Go API Setup", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-5/opencode-go-api" }}
    next={{ label: "Workflow 2: Log Analysis", href: "/en/aiops-lab/phase-5/workflow-2-log-analysis" }}
>
    <div class="docs-page">
        <div class="f5-hero"><div class="f5-hero__top"><div class="f5-hero__badge">Phase 5.1</div><span class="f5-hero__time">Workflow 1</span></div><h1 class="f5-hero__title">Incident Response<span class="f5-hero__accent"> · Alerta → LLM → Discord</span></h1><p class="f5-hero__subtitle">El workflow mas importante del proyecto. Alertmanager dispara un webhook en n8n cuando una alerta se activa. n8n extrae el contexto, consulta al LLM para analisis de causa raiz y envia el resultado a Discord. Todo en menos de 15 segundos.</p></div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">01</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Flujo del Workflow</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Cuatro nodos encadenados. El trigger es un webhook — no hay polling, no hay cron. Alertmanager empuja la alerta a n8n en tiempo real.</p>
            <div class="flow-viz">
                <div class="flow-box flow-box--trigger">Alertmanager</div>
                <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
                <div class="flow-box flow-box--webhook">Webhook</div>
                <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
                <div class="flow-box flow-box--transform">Set</div>
                <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
                <div class="flow-box flow-box--llm">LLM</div>
                <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
                <div class="flow-box flow-box--discord">Discord</div>
            </div>
            <div class="nodes-list">
                {nodes.map((n) => (
                    <div class="node-card">
                        <div class="node-card__header"><div class="node-card__num">{n.num}</div><div class="node-card__meta"><span class="node-card__type">{n.type}</span><span class="node-card__name">{n.name}</span></div></div>
                        <p class="node-card__desc">{n.desc}</p>
                        <div class="node-card__detail">{n.detail}</div>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">02</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Configuracion de Alertmanager</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Para que este workflow funcione, Alertmanager debe estar configurado para enviar alertas al webhook de n8n. Esto se configuro en la Phase 4.</p>
            <div class="code-block"><div class="code-block__header"><span class="code-block__file">alertmanager/configmap.yml</span></div>
                <pre><code>receivers:
  - name: n8n-webhook
    webhook_configs:
      - url: http://n8n.aiops.svc.cluster.local:5678/webhook/alertmanager
        send_resolved: true

route:
  receiver: n8n-webhook
  group_wait: 10s
  group_interval: 30s
  repeat_interval: 4h</code></pre>
            </div>
            <p class="overview-text"><code>send_resolved: true</code> es clave: cuando una alerta se resuelve, Alertmanager envia una segunda notificacion. El workflow detecta el status resolved y cambia el color del embed de Discord de rojo a verde. El incidente se documenta con apertura y cierre.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section">
            <div class="section-header"><span class="section-num">03</span><h2 class="overview-h2">Testear el Workflow</h2></div>
            <p class="overview-lead">Para probar el flujo sin esperar una alerta real, se puede disparar una alerta manualmente desde Alertmanager.</p>
            <div class="terminal-block"><div class="terminal-block__bar"><div class="terminal-block__dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span class="terminal-block__title">disparar alerta manual</span></div><div class="terminal-block__body">
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># Disparar alerta de prueba</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-prompt">$</span><span class="t-cmd">kubectl exec -n aiops deploy/alertmanager -- amtool alert add \</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-cmd">  alertname=TestIncident severity=critical \</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-cmd">  --annotation=description="Pod crashed unexpectedly"</span></div>
                <div class="t-line t-line--spacer"></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># Verificar que n8n recibio la alerta</span></div>
                <div class="t-line"><span class="t-comment"># UI n8n → Executions → ver el ultimo run</span></div>
            </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="overview-section overview-section--cta">
            <div class="cta-card"><div class="cta-card__content"><h3 class="cta-card__title">Siguiente: Workflow 2 — Log Analysis</h3><p class="cta-card__desc">El segundo workflow consulta Loki periodicamente, analiza logs de error con LLM y genera reportes de salud del sistema.</p></div><a href="/en/aiops-lab/phase-5/workflow-2-log-analysis" class="cta-card__btn"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.5 2v6h-6M2.5 22v-6h6M2 11.5a10 10 0 0118.8-4.3M22 12.5a10 10 0 01-18.8 4.2"/></svg>Workflow 2</a></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style is:global>
    .docs-page { max-width: 740px; }
    .f5-hero { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.875rem; padding: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .f5-hero__top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .f5-hero__badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-300); padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .f5-hero__time { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-dim); padding: 0.35rem 0.65rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .f5-hero__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-50); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .f5-hero__accent { color: var(--green-500); font-weight: 500; }
    .f5-hero__subtitle { font-size: var(--text-md); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 560px; }
    .overview-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; } .overview-section--cta { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .section-num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--green-600); font-weight: 500; }
    .overview-h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0; }
    .overview-lead { font-size: var(--text-base); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; max-width: 560px; }
    .overview-text { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .overview-text code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; color: var(--green-300); }
    .flow-viz { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    .flow-box { padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .flow-box--trigger { background: rgba(234,179,8,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(234,179,8,0.25); color: #eab308; }
    .flow-box--webhook { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.2); color: var(--green-300); }
    .flow-box--transform { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim); }
    .flow-box--llm { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2); color: #3b82f6; }
    .flow-box--discord { background: rgba(88,101,242,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(88,101,242,0.2); color: #5865f2; }
    .flow-arr { color: var(--green-500); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .nodes-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .node-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem; }
    .node-card__header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .node-card__num { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 1.5rem; height: 1.5rem; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-2xs); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-400); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .node-card__meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
    .node-card__type { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-3xs); color: var(--text-dim); padding: 0.1rem 0.3rem; border-radius: 0.2rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .node-card__name { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-300); }
    .node-card__desc { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .node-card__detail { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.45; padding-top: 0.35rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .code-block { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .code-block__header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0.45rem 0.85rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .code-block__file { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-2xs); color: var(--text-dim); }
    .code-block pre { margin: 0; padding: 0.85rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    .code-block code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
    .terminal-block { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.6rem; overflow: hidden; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-xs); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .terminal-block__bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.025); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .terminal-block__dots { display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; }
    .terminal-block__dots span { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); display: block; }
    .terminal-block__title { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: var(--text-2xs); margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-right: 2.5rem; }
    .terminal-block__body { padding: 0.65rem 0.85rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.1rem; }
    .t-line { line-height: 1.5; } .t-line--spacer { height: 0.35rem; }
    .t-prompt { color: var(--green-600); margin-right: 0.3rem; }
    .t-cmd { color: var(--green-300); }
    .t-out { color: var(--text-dim); padding-left: 0; }
    .t-comment { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); font-style: italic; }
    .cta-card { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-card__content { flex: 1; }
    .cta-card__title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-base); font-weight: 600; color: var(--green-50); margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
    .cta-card__desc { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
    .cta-card__btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 500; color: var(--green-50); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
    .cta-card__btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: var(--border-hover); }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .flow-viz { flex-direction: column; } .flow-arr { display: none; } .cta-card { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; } }
</style>
